  "Description": "Called By: SbcIdsProdQhpExtCntl\n\nProcess Description: Job loads data from sequential file to PROD_QHP table\n\nMODIFICATIONS:\n                                                                                                                                                                                                               DATASTAGE               CODE                           DATE\nDEVELOPER             DATE                PROJECT                     DESCRIPTION                                                                                      ENVIRONMENT          REVIEWER                 REVIEW\n-----------------------------    ----------------------     ------------------------------        -----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------  ------------------------------    ------------------------------       --------------------\nJaideep Mankala      2016-07-22              5605                             Original Programming                                                                       IntegrateDev2             Kalyan Neelam              2016-08-10\n\nAnnotations:\nRead Load File created in the FKEY job\nCopy Stage for buffer\nTruncate and Insert records to PROD_QHP table"
}